{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/tools/layout,_N_T_/tools/ocr-scanner/layout,_N_T_/tools/ocr-scanner/page,_N_T_/tools/ocr-scanner"},"segmentPaths":["/_tree","/_full","/tools/ocr-scanner/__PAGE__","/tools/ocr-scanner","/tools","/_index","/_head"]},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\" class=\"geist_a71539c9-module__T19VSG__variable geist_mono_8d43a2aa-module__8Li5zG__variable h-full\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/797e433ab948586e-s.p.09zddjkbdep5a.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/caa3a2e1cccd8315-s.p.09~u27dqhyhd6.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/123doanyjnwwq.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/04uuf1716ltqa.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/0eyplc079uusk.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0tszvp5wpnn-t.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0bss4aof7q0cj.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0hi511ipeys_s.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/turbopack-13rn3bqw7ype6.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0zif8_3mgcc0x.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0zv.me6xdrdsz.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0ag6f0zogt0qg.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/04p0ygcx_g620.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0_pa1c_tsbiw0.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/10nuyoal1pib2.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/11~hh-yuwxxvh.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/15fv-g-ryqf4b.js\" async=\"\"></script><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://www.highperformanceformat.com\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"/><link rel=\"dns-prefetch\" href=\"https://www.highperformanceformat.com\"/><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://pl29142630.profitablecpmratenetwork.com\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"/><link rel=\"dns-prefetch\" href=\"https://pl29142630.profitablecpmratenetwork.com\"/><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><title>Free OCR Scanner Online — No Sign Up | Free Tool Shed</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Extract text from images and scanned PDFs using OCR. Supports 15+ languages with instant export to .txt, .docx, and searchable PDF. A free alternative to Adobe Acrobat. No sign up required.\"/><meta name=\"google-adsense-account\" content=\"ca-pub-7700405385978151\"/><link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://freetoolshed.com/tools/ocr-scanner\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Free OCR Scanner Online — No Sign Up | Free Tool Shed\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Extract text from images and scanned PDFs using OCR. Supports 15+ languages with instant export to .txt, .docx, and searchable PDF. A free alternative to Adobe Acrobat. No sign up required.\"/><meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://freetoolshed.com/tools/ocr-scanner\"/><meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Free Tool Shed\"/><meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://freetoolshed.com/screenshots/ocr-scanner.png\"/><meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"1440\"/><meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"900\"/><meta property=\"og:image:alt\" content=\"OCR Scanner workspace screenshot\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Free OCR Scanner Online — No Sign Up | Free Tool Shed\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Extract text from images and scanned PDFs using OCR. Supports 15+ languages with instant export to .txt, .docx, and searchable PDF. A free alternative to Adobe Acrobat. No sign up required.\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://freetoolshed.com/screenshots/ocr-scanner.png\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.0x3dzn~oxb6tn.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\"/><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Free Tool Shed\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com\",\"logo\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/og-image.png\",\"description\":\"Free, browser-based tools that replace paid software. No sign up, no downloads, no servers — every tool runs client-side.\",\"founder\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"James Nicolaus\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/about\"}}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"WebSite\",\"name\":\"Free Tool Shed\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com\",\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Free Tool Shed\"}}</script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/03~yq9q893hmn.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"flex min-h-full flex-col antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><script>((a,b,c,d,e,f,g,h)=>{let i=document.documentElement,j=[\"light\",\"dark\"];function k(b){var c;(Array.isArray(a)?a:[a]).forEach(a=>{let c=\"class\"===a,d=c&&f?e.map(a=>f[a]||a):e;c?(i.classList.remove(...d),i.classList.add(f&&f[b]?f[b]:b)):i.setAttribute(a,b)}),c=b,h&&j.includes(c)&&(i.style.colorScheme=c)}if(d)k(d);else try{let a=localStorage.getItem(b)||c,d=g&&\"system\"===a?window.matchMedia(\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\").matches?\"dark\":\"light\":a;k(d)}catch(a){}})(\"class\",\"theme\",\"system\",null,[\"light\",\"dark\"],null,true,true)</script><nav class=\"sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-border bg-background/95 backdrop-blur supports-[backdrop-filter]:bg-background/60\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex h-14 max-w-7xl items-center justify-between px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 font-heading text-lg font-semibold\" href=\"/\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-wrench size-5 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.106-3.105c.32-.322.863-.22.983.218a6 6 0 0 1-8.259 7.057l-7.91 7.91a1 1 0 0 1-2.999-3l7.91-7.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.057-8.259c.438.12.54.662.219.984z\"></path></svg><span>Free Tool Shed</span></a><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><a class=\"rounded-md px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a><button type=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" data-slot=\"button\" aria-label=\"Toggle theme\" class=\"group/button inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-transparent bg-clip-padding text-sm font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition-all outline-none select-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-3 focus-visible:ring-ring/50 active:translate-y-px disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 aria-invalid:border-destructive aria-invalid:ring-3 aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:border-destructive/50 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 [&amp;_svg:not([class*=&#x27;size-&#x27;])]:size-4 hover:bg-muted hover:text-foreground aria-expanded:bg-muted aria-expanded:text-foreground dark:hover:bg-muted/50 size-8\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sun size-4 scale-100 rotate-0 transition-all dark:scale-0 dark:-rotate-90\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M12 20v2\"></path><path d=\"m4.93 4.93 1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"m17.66 17.66 1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 12h2\"></path><path d=\"m6.34 17.66-1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"m19.07 4.93-1.41 1.41\"></path></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-moon absolute size-4 scale-0 rotate-90 transition-all dark:scale-100 dark:rotate-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20.985 12.486a9 9 0 1 1-9.473-9.472c.405-.022.617.46.402.803a6 6 0 0 0 8.268 8.268c.344-.215.825-.004.803.401\"></path></svg></button></div></div></nav><div class=\"flex flex-1 flex-col\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl flex-1 px-4 py-6 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"flex gap-6\"><main class=\"min-w-0 flex-1\"><div class=\"mb-4 hidden justify-center lg:flex\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded \" style=\"width:728px;height:90px;max-width:100%\" data-ad-slot=\"leaderboard\"></div></div><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"SoftwareApplication\",\"name\":\"Free OCR Scanner\",\"description\":\"Extract text from images and scanned PDFs using OCR. Supports 15+ languages with instant export to .txt, .docx, and searchable PDF.\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/tools/ocr-scanner\",\"applicationCategory\":\"UtilitiesApplication\",\"operatingSystem\":\"Web\",\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"Offer\",\"price\":\"0\",\"priceCurrency\":\"USD\"}}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"HowTo\",\"name\":\"How to Extract Text from an Image or PDF\",\"description\":\"Run OCR on images or scanned PDFs in the browser, then export the text as TXT, DOCX, or a searchable PDF.\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/tools/ocr-scanner\",\"step\":[{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"1. Upload your file\",\"text\":\"Drag and drop an image or scanned PDF onto the upload area, or click to browse. You can add multiple files at once — images and PDFs can be mixed. Each PDF page is automatically rendered as an image for OCR processing.\"},{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"2. Choose your language\",\"text\":\"Select the OCR language from the dropdown in the toolbar. The default is English, but you can switch to any of the 15+ supported languages including French, German, Spanish, Chinese, Japanese, Arabic, and Hindi. The OCR engine reinitializes automatically when you change languages.\"},{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"3. Review and edit the text\",\"text\":\"Once processing completes, the extracted text appears in the right panel. The text is fully editable — fix any OCR errors, remove headers or footers, or reformat the content. Word and character counts update as you type.\"},{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"position\":4,\"name\":\"4. Export the result\",\"text\":\"Choose your export format: Plain Text (.txt) for simple text, Word Document (.docx) for formatted output with page separators, or Searchable PDF to create a PDF with your original scan plus an invisible text layer for search and selection. Click Download or use Copy Text for the clipboard.\"}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is this OCR tool really free?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes, completely free. No hidden fees, no premium tiers, and no sign-up required. The tool is ad-supported so it can remain free for everyone.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How do I extract text from an image?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Drop your image (PNG, JPG, TIFF, BMP, or WebP) onto the editor. OCR runs automatically in your browser and displays the extracted text in seconds. You can then copy it or export as .txt, .docx, or searchable PDF.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can I extract text from a scanned PDF?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes. Drop a scanned PDF and each page is rendered and processed with OCR. Multi-page PDFs are fully supported with sequential page processing.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What languages are supported?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Over 15 languages including English, Spanish, French, German, Italian, Portuguese, Dutch, Polish, Russian, Japanese, Korean, Chinese (Simplified and Traditional), Arabic, and Hindi.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is my data private?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes. All OCR processing happens locally in your browser using WebAssembly. Your images and PDFs are never uploaded to any server.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What export formats are available?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Export extracted text as plain text (.txt), Word document (.docx), or searchable PDF with an invisible text layer over the original scan.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Do I need to install anything?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"No. The OCR engine runs entirely in your browser via WebAssembly. No desktop app, no plugins, no extensions. Open the page and start scanning.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How accurate is the OCR?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Accuracy depends on image quality. Clean, high-resolution scans (300+ DPI) typically achieve 95%+ accuracy. The tool shows a confidence score for each processed page so you can verify results.\"}}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"OCR Scanner\"}]}</script><nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\" class=\"mb-4\"><ol class=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right size-3.5 shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-foreground\">OCR Scanner</span></li></ol></nav><h1 class=\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Free OCR Scanner — Image &amp; PDF to Text</h1><p class=\"mt-2 text-lg text-muted-foreground\">Extract text from images and scanned PDFs instantly — a free alternative to Adobe Acrobat OCR and ABBYY FineReader. No sign-up required.</p><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"James Nicolaus\",\"jobTitle\":\"Builder & Maintainer, Free Tool Shed\",\"description\":\"James Nicolaus builds and maintains every tool on Free Tool Shed. Each tool is designed, tested in real browsers across desktop and mobile, and shipped only after handling the messy edge cases — large files, slow connections, unusual inputs — that paid alternatives often hide behind sign-up walls.\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/about\",\"worksFor\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Free Tool Shed\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com\"}}</script><p class=\"mt-3 text-xs text-muted-foreground\">Built and maintained by<!-- --> <a class=\"font-medium text-foreground underline-offset-4 hover:underline\" rel=\"author\" href=\"/about\">James Nicolaus</a></p><section aria-label=\"Summary\" class=\"mt-6 rounded-lg border border-brand/30 bg-brand/5 p-4\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground\">Free Tool Shed&#x27;s OCR Scanner extracts text from images and scanned PDFs locally in your browser using Tesseract — no upload, no sign-up. Supports 15+ languages, multi-page PDFs, and exports to plain text, .docx, or a searchable PDF that preserves the original page layout. A free alternative to Adobe Acrobat OCR and ABBYY FineReader.</p></section><div class=\"mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><h2 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Instant Text Extraction</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Drop an image or scanned PDF, get editable text in seconds. Powered by tesseract.js OCR running entirely in your browser.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><h2 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">15+ Languages Supported</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">English, Spanish, French, German, Chinese, Japanese, Arabic, and more. Switch languages with one click.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><h2 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Multiple Export Formats</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Copy text, download as .txt or .docx, or create a searchable PDF with an invisible text layer over your original scan.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><h2 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">100% Private, No Upload</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">All OCR processing happens in your browser using WebAssembly. Your files never leave your device.</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-8\"><!--$!--><template data-dgst=\"BAILOUT_TO_CLIENT_SIDE_RENDERING\"></template><!--/$--></div><div class=\"my-8 flex justify-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded \" style=\"width:728px;height:90px;max-width:100%\" data-ad-slot=\"mid-content\"></div></div><div class=\"mt-16 space-y-12\"><div data-orientation=\"horizontal\" role=\"separator\" aria-orientation=\"horizontal\" data-slot=\"separator\" class=\"shrink-0 bg-border data-horizontal:h-px data-horizontal:w-full data-vertical:w-px data-vertical:self-stretch\"></div><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold\">Free OCR — Extract Text from Images &amp; Scanned PDFs</h2><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\">Scanned documents, photos of receipts, screenshots with text — they all contain information you can&#x27;t copy-paste. Until now, extracting that text meant paying for Adobe Acrobat ($22.99/month) or ABBYY FineReader ($199 one-time). Free Tool Shed&#x27;s OCR Scanner does the same thing for free, right in your browser. Drop a file, get editable text in seconds. No account, no install, no upload to a server.</p><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\">The tool uses tesseract.js — the same Tesseract OCR engine that powers Google&#x27;s document scanning — compiled to WebAssembly so it runs entirely on your machine. Your files never leave your device. It supports 15+ languages, handles multi-page PDFs, and exports to plain text, Word documents, or searchable PDFs with an invisible text layer over your original scan.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Features</h2><ul class=\"mt-4 grid gap-x-8 gap-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground sm:grid-cols-2\"><li>Drag-and-drop image upload (PNG, JPG, TIFF, BMP, WebP)</li><li>Scanned PDF support — each page rendered and OCR&#x27;d</li><li>15+ OCR languages (English, French, German, Spanish, and more)</li><li>Batch processing — add multiple files at once</li><li>Real-time progress tracking per page</li><li>Confidence score for each recognized page</li><li>Editable text output — fix errors before exporting</li><li>Word and character count in real time</li><li>Export as plain text (.txt)</li><li>Export as Word document (.docx) with page separators</li><li>Export as searchable PDF with invisible text overlay</li><li>Copy extracted text to clipboard</li><li>Re-OCR all pages with a different language</li><li>File thumbnails with per-page status indicators</li><li>Language and export format preferences saved across sessions</li><li>Max 50 MB per file, up to 50 PDF pages</li><li>100% client-side — files never leave your browser</li><li>Powered by tesseract.js WebAssembly engine</li></ul></section><section><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">How to Extract Text from an Image or PDF (4 Steps)</h2><ol class=\"mt-4 space-y-4\"><li><p class=\"font-medium\">1. Upload your file</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Drag and drop an image or scanned PDF onto the upload area, or click to browse. You can add multiple files at once — images and PDFs can be mixed. Each PDF page is automatically rendered as an image for OCR processing.</p></li><li><p class=\"font-medium\">2. Choose your language</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Select the OCR language from the dropdown in the toolbar. The default is English, but you can switch to any of the 15+ supported languages including French, German, Spanish, Chinese, Japanese, Arabic, and Hindi. The OCR engine reinitializes automatically when you change languages.</p></li><li><p class=\"font-medium\">3. Review and edit the text</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Once processing completes, the extracted text appears in the right panel. The text is fully editable — fix any OCR errors, remove headers or footers, or reformat the content. Word and character counts update as you type.</p></li><li><p class=\"font-medium\">4. Export the result</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Choose your export format: Plain Text (.txt) for simple text, Word Document (.docx) for formatted output with page separators, or Searchable PDF to create a PDF with your original scan plus an invisible text layer for search and selection. Click Download or use Copy Text for the clipboard.</p></li></ol></section><section aria-labelledby=\"tool-insights-tips\"><h2 id=\"tool-insights-tips\" class=\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Tips from Building <!-- -->the OCR Scanner</h2><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\">Notes from designing and testing this tool — what we kept in mind, the edge cases we worked around, and the small choices that make the difference between a tool that ships and one that breaks on real input.</p><ul class=\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\"><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\"></path><path d=\"M9 18h6\"></path><path d=\"M10 22h4\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Higher resolution beats fancier post-processing</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">OCR accuracy scales directly with input resolution up to about 300 DPI. A clean 300-DPI scan outperforms a heavily-processed 150-DPI scan every time. Re-scan rather than upscale.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\"></path><path d=\"M9 18h6\"></path><path d=\"M10 22h4\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Pick the right language pack</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Tesseract loads a separate model per language. The English model can&#x27;t read German umlauts or Cyrillic characters. Select the language(s) actually present in the document before scanning.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\"></path><path d=\"M9 18h6\"></path><path d=\"M10 22h4\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Use searchable PDF for archives, .txt for editing</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Searchable PDFs preserve the original page layout with a text layer underneath — great for archives. Plain .txt strips all formatting and is better when you&#x27;ll re-flow the text in another editor.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\"></path><path d=\"M9 18h6\"></path><path d=\"M10 22h4\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Pre-crop pages before scanning</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">OCR runs on the whole image, including borders, page numbers, and printer marks. Cropping to just the body text speeds up processing and reduces false matches on edge artifacts.</p></div></li></ul></section><section aria-labelledby=\"tool-insights-mistakes\"><h2 id=\"tool-insights-mistakes\" class=\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Common Mistakes to Avoid</h2><ul class=\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\"><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\"></path><path d=\"M12 9v4\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Scanning at 96 DPI from a screenshot</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Screenshots of text are usually 72–96 DPI, far below OCR&#x27;s accuracy threshold. Capture at higher resolution or rescan the original document.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\"></path><path d=\"M12 9v4\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Mixing multiple languages in one pass</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Running an English-only model over a bilingual page drops the non-English text entirely. Either select both languages or process pages separately.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\"></path><path d=\"M12 9v4\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Trusting OCR on handwriting or stylized fonts</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Tesseract is trained for print fonts. Cursive handwriting, decorative scripts, and heavy stylization produce unreliable output. For handwriting, expect manual cleanup.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\"></path><path d=\"M12 9v4\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Skipping page rotation</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">A landscape page scanned in portrait orientation will OCR as gibberish. Rotate before scanning, or use a scanner setting that auto-orients.</p></div></li></ul></section><section aria-labelledby=\"tool-insights-takeaways\" class=\"rounded-lg border border-brand/30 bg-brand/5 p-5\"><h2 id=\"tool-insights-takeaways\" class=\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight\">Key Takeaways</h2><ul class=\"mt-3 space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm text-foreground\">The OCR Scanner runs Tesseract locally in your browser — images and PDFs never upload.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm text-foreground\">It supports 15+ languages, multi-page PDFs, and exports to .txt, .docx, or a searchable PDF.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm text-foreground\">Accuracy depends heavily on input quality: 300 DPI clean scans, correct language pack, correct orientation.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm text-foreground\">It is a free alternative to Adobe Acrobat OCR and ABBYY FineReader for routine document scanning.</span></li></ul></section><section><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Free Adobe Acrobat OCR Alternative</h2><div class=\"mt-4 overflow-x-auto\"><table class=\"w-full min-w-[600px] border-collapse text-sm\"><thead><tr class=\"border-b border-border text-left\"><th class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-semibold\">Feature</th><th class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-semibold\">Free Tool Shed</th><th class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-semibold\">Adobe Acrobat</th><th class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-semibold\">ABBYY FineReader</th><th class=\"py-2 font-semibold\">Google Drive OCR</th></tr></thead><tbody class=\"text-muted-foreground\"><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Price</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">Free forever</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">$22.99/mo</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">$199 one-time</td><td class=\"py-2  \">Free (with limits)</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Installation</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">None (browser)</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Desktop app</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Desktop app</td><td class=\"py-2  \">None (web)</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Account Required</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">No</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes (Adobe ID)</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2  \">Yes (Google)</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Image OCR</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2  \">Yes</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">PDF OCR</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2  \">Yes (Google Docs)</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Languages</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">15+</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">20+</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">200+</td><td class=\"py-2  \">200+</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Batch Processing</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2  \">No</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Searchable PDF Export</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2  \">No</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Word (.docx) Export</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2  \">Yes</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Editable Output</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Limited</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2  \">Yes (in Docs)</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Handwriting Recognition</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">Basic</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Advanced</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Advanced</td><td class=\"py-2  \">Basic</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Table Recognition</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">No</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Advanced</td><td class=\"py-2  \">Basic</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Data Privacy</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">Client-side only</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Cloud upload</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Local</td><td class=\"py-2  \">Cloud upload</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border/50\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Offline Support</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground\">Yes (after load)</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 \">Yes</td><td class=\"py-2  \">No</td></tr></tbody></table></div></section><section><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class=\"mt-4 space-y-3\"><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium\">Is this OCR tool really free?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Yes, completely free. No hidden fees, no premium tiers, and no sign-up required. The tool is ad-supported so it can remain free for everyone.</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium\">Do my files get uploaded to a server?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">No. All OCR processing runs locally in your browser using WebAssembly (tesseract.js). Your images and PDFs never leave your device. There is no server-side component — the page works even offline once loaded.</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium\">How accurate is the OCR?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">For clean scans and printed text, expect 90–99% accuracy depending on font quality, resolution, and contrast. Handwritten text, heavily skewed images, or very low-resolution scans may produce lower accuracy. Higher-resolution input images (300 DPI+) give the best results.</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium\">What languages are supported?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">15+ languages: English, French, German, Spanish, Italian, Portuguese, Dutch, Polish, Russian, Japanese, Korean, Chinese (Simplified and Traditional), Arabic, and Hindi. Select the language from the toolbar dropdown before processing.</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium\">Can I OCR a multi-page PDF?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Yes. Drop a PDF file and each page is automatically rendered as an image and OCR&#x27;d individually. The tool supports up to 50 pages per PDF. All page text is combined with page separators in the output.</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium\">What is a searchable PDF?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">A searchable PDF contains your original scanned image with an invisible text layer placed on top. This means the PDF looks exactly like the original scan, but you can select, search, and copy text from it. It&#x27;s the standard output format of professional OCR software.</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium\">How do I get the best OCR results?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Use high-resolution scans (300 DPI or higher), ensure the text is not skewed or rotated, and use good contrast (dark text on light background). For photos, make sure the text is in focus and evenly lit. Select the correct language before processing.</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium\">Can I edit the extracted text?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Yes. The text output panel is fully editable. Fix any OCR errors, remove unwanted headers or footers, or reformat the content before exporting. Word and character counts update in real time as you type.</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium\">Why use this instead of Adobe Acrobat?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Adobe Acrobat costs $22.99/month and requires a desktop installation plus an Adobe ID. This tool is free, runs in your browser, needs no account, and keeps your files private (no cloud upload). For basic OCR tasks — extracting text from scans, converting images to text, creating searchable PDFs — it does the same job at zero cost.</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium\">Is there a file size limit?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">The maximum file size is 50 MB per file, and PDFs are limited to 50 pages. These limits exist to prevent browser memory issues. For most scanned documents and images, this is more than enough.</p></details></div></section></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><aside class=\"hidden w-[300px] shrink-0 lg:block\"><div class=\"sticky top-20\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded \" style=\"width:300px;height:250px;max-width:100%\" data-ad-slot=\"sidebar\"></div><div id=\"tool-guide-portal\"></div></div></aside></div></div></div><footer class=\"border-t border-border bg-muted/40\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex max-w-7xl flex-col items-center gap-4 px-4 py-8 sm:flex-row sm:justify-between sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> Free Tool Shed. All rights reserved.</p><nav class=\"flex gap-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy</a><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/terms\">Terms</a></nav></div></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0eyplc079uusk.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).