op and mobile, and shipped only after handling the messy edge cases — large files, slow connections, unusual inputs — that paid alternatives often hide behind sign-up walls.\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://freetoolshed.com/about\\\",\\\"worksFor\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Organization\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Free Tool Shed\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://freetoolshed.com\\\"}}\"}}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 text-xs text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":[\"Built and maintained by\",\" \",[\"$\",\"$L4\",null,{\"href\":\"/about\",\"className\":\"font-medium text-foreground underline-offset-4 hover:underline\",\"rel\":\"author\",\"children\":\"James Nicolaus\"}],\"$undefined\"]}]]\n1d:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-label\":\"Summary\",\"className\":\"mt-6 rounded-lg border border-brand/30 bg-brand/5 p-4\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground\",\"children\":\"Free Tool Shed's OCR Scanner extracts text from images and scanned PDFs locally in your browser using Tesseract — no upload, no sign-up. Supports 15+ languages, multi-page PDFs, and exports to plain text, .docx, or a searchable PDF that preserves the original page layout. A free alternative to Adobe Acrobat OCR and ABBYY FineReader.\"}]}]\n1e:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Instant Text Extraction\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Drop an image or scanned PDF, get editable text in seconds. Powered by tesseract.js OCR running entirely in your browser.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"15+ Languages Supported\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"English, Spanish, French, German, Chinese, Japanese, Arabic, and more. Switch languages with one click.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Multiple Export Formats\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Copy text, download as .txt or .docx, or create a searchable PDF with an invisible text layer over your original scan.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"100% Private, No Upload\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"All OCR processing happens in your browser using WebAssembly. Your files never leave your device.\"}]]}]]}]\n1f:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-8\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L2a\",null,{}]}]\n20:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"my-8 flex justify-center\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L16\",null,{\"slot\":\"mid-content\"}]}]\n21:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-16 space-y-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L2b\",null,{}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Free OCR — Extract Text from Images & Scanned PDFs\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Scanned documents, photos of receipts, screenshots with text — they all contain information you can't copy-paste. Until now, extracting that text meant paying for Adobe Acrobat ($22.99/month) or ABBYY FineReader ($199 one-time). Free Tool Shed's OCR Scanner does the same thing for free, right in your browser. Drop a file, get editable text in seconds. No account, no install, no upload to a server.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"The tool uses tesseract.js — the same Tesseract OCR engine that powers Google's document scanning — compiled to WebAssembly so it runs entirely on your machine. Your files never leave your device. It supports 15+ languages, handles multi-page PDFs, and exports to plain text, Word documents, or searchable PDFs with an invisible text layer over your original scan.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xl font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Features\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid gap-x-8 gap-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground sm:grid-cols-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Drag-and-drop image upload (PNG, JPG, TIFF, BMP, WebP)\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Scanned PDF support — each page rendered and OCR'd\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"15+ OCR languages (English, French, German, Spanish, and more)\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Batch processing — add multiple files at once\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Real-time progress tracking per page\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Confidence score for each recognized page\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Editable text output — fix errors before exporting\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Word and character count in real time\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Export as plain text (.txt)\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Export as Word document (.docx) with page separators\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Export as searchable PDF with invisible text overlay\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Copy extracted text to clipboard\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Re-OCR all pages with a different language\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"File thumbnails with per-page status indicators\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Language and export format preferences saved across sessions\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Max 50 MB per file, up to 50 PDF pages\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"100% client-side — files never leave your browser\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Powered by tesseract.js WebAssembly engine\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xl font-semibold\",\"children\":\"How to Extract Text from an Image or PDF (4 Steps)\"}],[\"$\",\"ol\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"1. Upload your file\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"font-medium\",\"children\":\"1. Upload your file\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Drag and drop an image or scanned PDF onto the upload area, or click to browse. You can add multiple files at once — images and PDFs can be mixed. Each PDF page is automatically rendered as an image for OCR processing.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"2. Choose your language\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"font-medium\",\"children\":\"2. Choose your language\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Select the OCR language from the dropdown in the toolbar. The default is English, but you can switch to any of the 15+ supported languages including French, German, Spanish, Chinese, Japanese, Arabic, and Hindi. The OCR engine reinitializes automatically when you change languages.\"}]]}],\"$L2c\",\"$L2d\"]}]]}],\"$L2e\",\"$L2f\",\"$L30\"]}]\n22:[\"$\",\"script\",\"script-0\",{\"src\":\"/_next/static/chunks/15fv-g-ryqf4b.js\",\"async\":true,\"nonce\":\"$undefined\"}]\n23:[\"$\",\"$L31\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$28\",null,{\"name\":\"Next.MetadataOutlet\",\"children\":\"$@32\"}]}]\n2c:[\"$\",\"li\",\"3. Review and edit the text\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"font-medium\",\"children\":\"3. Review and edit the text\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Once processing completes, the extracted text appears in the right panel. The text is fully editable — fix any OCR errors, remove headers or footers, or reformat the content. Word and character counts update as you type.\"}]]}]\n2d:[\"$\",\"li\",\"4. Export the result\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"font-medium\",\"children\":\"4. Export the result\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Choose your export format: Plain Text (.txt) for simple text, Word Document (.docx) for formatted output with page separators, or Searchable PDF to create a PDF with your original scan plus an invisible text layer for search and selection. Click Download or use Copy Text for the clipboard.\"}]]}]\n2e:[[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-labelledby\":\"tool-insights-tips\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"tool-insights-tips\",\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":[\"Tips from Building \",\"the OCR Scanner\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Notes from designing and testing this tool — what we kept in mind, the edge cases we worked around, and the small choices that make the difference between a tool that ships and one that breaks on real input.\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"Higher resolution beats fancier post-processing\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\",\"key\":\"1gvzjb\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M9 18h6\",\"key\":\"x1upvd\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M10 22h4\",\"key\":\"ceow96\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Higher resolution beats fancier post-processing\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"OCR accuracy scales directly with input resolution up to about 300 DPI. A clean 300-DPI scan outperforms a heavily-processed 150-DPI scan every time. Re-scan rather than upscale.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Pick the right language pack\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$2e:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Pick the right language pack\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Tesseract loads a separate model per language. The English model can't read German umlauts or Cyrillic characters. Select the language(s) actually present in the document before scanning.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Use searchable PDF for archives, .txt for editing\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$2e:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Use searchable PDF for archives, .txt for editing\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Searchable PDFs preserve the original page layout with a text layer underneath — great for archives. Plain .txt strips all formatting and is better when you'll re-flow the text in another editor.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Pre-crop pages before scanning\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$2e:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Pre-crop pages before scanning\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"OCR runs on the whole image, including borders, page numbers, and printer marks. Cropping to just the body text speeds up processing and reduces false matches on edge artifacts.\"}]]}]]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-labelledby\":\"tool-insights-mistakes\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"tool-insights-mistakes\",\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Common Mistakes to Avoid\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"Scanning at 96 DPI from a screenshot\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\",\"key\":\"wmoenq\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M12 9v4\",\"key\":\"juzpu7\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M12 17h.01\",\"key\":\"p32p05\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\"}],\"$L33\"]}],\"$L34\",\"$L35\",\"$L36\"]}]]}],\"$L37\"]\n2f:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xl font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Free Adobe Acrobat OCR Alternative\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 overflow-x-auto\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"table\",null,{\"className\":\"w-full min-w-[600px] border-collapse text-sm\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"thead\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"tr\",null,{\"className\":\"border-b border-border text-left\",\"children\":