me\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"For clean scans and printed text, expect 90–99% accuracy depending on font quality, resolution, and contrast. Handwritten text, heavily skewed images, or very low-resolution scans may produce lower accuracy. Higher-resolution input images (300 DPI+) give the best results.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"What languages are supported?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"What languages are supported?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"15+ languages: English, French, German, Spanish, Italian, Portuguese, Dutch, Polish, Russian, Japanese, Korean, Chinese (Simplified and Traditional), Arabic, and Hindi. Select the language from the toolbar dropdown before processing.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"Can I OCR a multi-page PDF?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Can I OCR a multi-page PDF?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Yes. Drop a PDF file and each page is automatically rendered as an image and OCR'd individually. The tool supports up to 50 pages per PDF. All page text is combined with page separators in the output.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"What is a searchable PDF?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"What is a searchable PDF?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"A searchable PDF contains your original scanned image with an invisible text layer placed on top. This means the PDF looks exactly like the original scan, but you can select, search, and copy text from it. It's the standard output format of professional OCR software.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"How do I get the best OCR results?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"How do I get the best OCR results?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Use high-resolution scans (300 DPI or higher), ensure the text is not skewed or rotated, and use good contrast (dark text on light background). For photos, make sure the text is in focus and evenly lit. Select the correct language before processing.\"}]]}],\"$L28\",\"$L29\",\"$L2a\"]}]]}]\n1b:null\n1c:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Scanning at 96 DPI from a screenshot\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Screenshots of text are usually 72–96 DPI, far below OCR's accuracy threshold. Capture at higher resolution or rescan the original document.\"}]]}]\n1d:[\"$\",\"li\",\"Mixing multiple languages in one pass\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$16:1:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Mixing multiple languages in one pass\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Running an English-only model over a bilingual page drops the non-English text entirely. Either select both languages or process pages separately.\"}]]}]]}]\n1e:[\"$\",\"li\",\"Trusting OCR on handwriting or stylized fonts\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[